snippet.title: Medusa's Labyrinth Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/436110/

Medusa’s Labyrinth is a first person horror game with stealth elements set in Ancient Greece. Inspired by the mythos of old, we have created a dark world populated by mythological creatures. Medusa’s Labyrinth brings horror to one of the most recognizable and epic parts of history, stories that were written more than two thousand years ago that are still with us today.
